articles.title: At least 26 people killed as gunmen open fire on tourists in Kashmir beauty spot - CNN
articles.description: At least 26 people were killed and a dozen injured in a suspected terror attack in the disputed Himalayan region of Jammu and Kashmir on Tuesday, a rare assault on tourists in a region fraught by decades of insurgency and opposition to India’s rule.
